    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it's in absolutely pristine, showroom condition! I've pampered this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage, and it still looks and drives just like it's brand new. Not a single scratch or dent to be found! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated with total love and care, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
