    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, delivering power through a perfectly dialed factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with zero bushing deflection, and the engine bay is in concours condition. A rare find for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance and a pristine chassis.",
      "price": 48500.0,
