    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like gloss, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are no stone chips, scratches, or door dings to be found anywhere on the body. The alloy wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is an immaculate sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment, retaining its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records documenting every oil change and inspection performed by certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-quality example that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection. Includes two keys, all original manuals, and a clean title.",
